### List all active system roles (requires ROOT or SUPERADMIN session)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/system/roles

###

### Create SUPERADMIN (requires ROOT or SUPERADMIN session)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/system/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "super@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Create SUPERADMIN - email already in use
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/system/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "root@example.com",
  "password": "secret123"
}

### Revoke SUPERADMIN (requires ROOT or SUPERADMIN session)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/system/roles/{{roleId}}

### Revoke SUPERADMIN - role not found
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/system/roles/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
